relation: Darrow2 - #54 A day of fun turns into a nightmare as the evil forces make a personal attack on our poor heroes. Fortunately, there's still Reginald...right?

Darrow2 - #55 Ness battles his growing worry and frustration at his inability to protect Paula, while the Dept. Store Spook tries to make him even more angry. Uh, yeah...probably not the smartest of Giygas' minions.
Darrow2 - #56 Jeff and Ness approach the Dept. Store Spook, who has pushed Ness a little too far.
Darrow2 - #57 Ness busts into the office to confront the Spook while Jeff stays behind. Although this may be bad for Jeff's panel time, it is good for his ability to remain alive.

Darrow2 - #58 A furious Ness unleashes his pent up rage, bringing a quick end to the Spook. Although he has no idea of what he's done, Ness has managed to tap into the highest power of Rockin' at this point. However, without being strong enough to control it, all he can manage is a generic beam attack that is a little bit weaker than the real thing.
